#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.linalg.inv.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.linalg.inv"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.inv.inv:1 of
msgid ""
"Compute the (multiplicative) inverse of a matrix. Given a square matrix "
"`a`, return the matrix `ainv` satisfying ``dot(a, ainv) = dot(ainv, a) = "
"eye(a.shape[0])``."
msgstr ""
"计算矩阵的（乘法）逆。给定一个方阵 `a`，返回满足 ``dot(a, ainv) = dot("
"ainv, a) = eye(a.shape[0])`` 的矩阵 `ainv`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.inv.inv of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.inv.inv:5 of
msgid "Matrix to be inverted."
msgstr "要进行求逆的矩阵。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.inv.inv:7 of
msgid "Return sparse value or not."
msgstr "是否返回稀疏值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.inv.inv of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.inv.inv:10 of
msgid "**ainv** -- (Multiplicative) inverse of the matrix `a`."
msgstr "**ainv** -- 矩阵 `a` 的（乘法）逆。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.inv.inv of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.inv.inv of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.inv.inv:13 of
msgid "If `a` is not square or inversion fails."
msgstr "如果 `a` 不是方阵或求逆失败。"

